overview: Official entry to the first Metro Manila Film Festival in 1979 directed by Emmanuel Borlaza and starred 	Jay Ilagan, Ronald Corveau, Rez Cortez, Anna Marin, Fred Montilla, Rosemarie Gil, Alicia Alonzo, Anita Linda, Romeo Rivera, Dino Kortes, Michael de Mesa, and Marissa del Mar.
title: Kadete
